data.description: Semi Custom Home that has been meticulously taken care of in the Foothills awaits your updating touches. High ceilings, lots of light, 2 fireplaces, granite counters in primary and guest bath and remote control ''black out'' metal sun screen for your Az. Room which looks out to your sparkling pool and large private lot. Mountain and City views, with large rooms, and a great floorplan. Additional 600+ sq.ft. detached garage has MANY possibilities with an additional private side door going out to flagstone patio and pool.Extra storage throughout.
